{"word":"G863 - ἀφίημι - aphíēmi - af-ee'-ay-mee - Cry","slug":"G863","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφίημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>aphíēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>af-ee'-ay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cry"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C6;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - aphie&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>af-ee'-ay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>hie&#x0304;mi</b> (to <i>send</i>; an intensive form of <b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x0342;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>eimi</b> (to <i>go</i>)); to <i>send forth</i>, in various applications: - cry, forgive, forsake, lay aside, leave, let (alone, be, go, have), omit, put (send) away, remit, suffer, yield up."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3929\">G3929</a>, <a href=\"#/G3935\">G3935</a>, <a href=\"#/G859\">G859</a>"}]}